Modem -&gt; router -&gt; switch -&gt; computers.
The router must be in front of the switch as the router assigns IP addresses to each device.
The wireless devices communicate with the router.
Run the Network Setup Wizard on each machine and turn on File and Printer Sharing on all devices.
Assign a Network name to be used by all devices.
Use WPA(2) for your wireless security.
Done.
